    Our story

    How we got our start?
    As a minimalist lifestyle brand that originated in 2008, TORRAS focuses on keeping things simple, providing people with ultra-sleek design, user-friendly and high-quality mobile digital products. We advocate a more "SIMPLE" attitude towards life while the world is changing swiftly.
    What makes our product unique?
    We draw inspiration from reality with a forward-looking design concept, innovate for an easier digital life and create an experience exceeds expectations for everyone. Simple in procedure but not character. Light in labor but not texture. You can enjoy the efforts at the details we make.
    Why we love what we do?
    Drawing inspiration from reality and fabricating the products carefully. We concern about the texture, the veins and the tactile experience of each product for creating unexpected surprises when it is close to the palm of each user. Let's Enjoy the SIMPLE, Touch the truth.

        4.0 out of 5 stars Not MagSafe compatible at all BUT it s a great cover
        Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2020
        Color: ClearVerified Purchase
        Let s be clear this cover is NOT MagSafe compatible. But it s the best cover if you don’t care about MagSafe.
        In order to be MagSafe compatible / certified, the cover needs to have the actual MagSafe magnets inside the cover otherwise the accessories won’t stick to it. Instead of reinforcing the MagSafe magnetic feature this cover creates a gap between the two which makes the accessory worthless. The accessory simply won’t stick to your iPhone strong enough or in some cases simply won’t stick at all. To claim this device is MagSafe is simply incorrect and a total waste of time if you want cross MagSafe accessories compatibility. We will be returning both covers.
        It works with wireless chargers including the MagSafe charger because of the wireless charging feature not because it s MagSafe. In fact you have to move it around on a MagSafe charger to find the right spot and it charges at a slower rate vs With a MagSafe certified compatible cover.
        **** Update 12/15 ****
        The cover will absolutely not work with the Apple MagSafe car mount or wallet. My wife likes it so much that she returned the MagSafe products instead of the cover !!!! I gave mine to a friend. That s why they deserve 4 stars despite the MagSafe incompatibility and their claim to contrary.

        Adam Callan
        5.0 out of 5 stars Great Clear Case!
        Reviewed in the United States on November 21, 2020
        Color: ClearVerified Purchase
        This case is very sturdy and fits the 12 Pro Max well. I thought the bottom was not fitting at first, but it actually contours so it is easier to swipe up from the bottom of the screen, which is well done. The kickstand is very high quality. I find myself moving it in and out of its satisfying click to secure the stand. The stand is as advertised in that is is tight enough so you can set it at a variety of angles, put it on both sides in vertical mode and it does work in portrait mode. Portrait is a little less sturdy, but fine is most uses. The back does show the color of your phone in good light, but at angles, the light is diffused so my blue phone does sometimes look space gray. Not a huge deal. The phone feels good in your hands, the different hardness of plastics are well placed, and buttons all click nicely.
        One thing that I would say could be an improvement is adding a magnet to the back so it works with MagSafe. The phone charges fine on a Qi charger and does kinda hold on my magnetic car mounts, but it is not as secure with a naked phone or adding a magnet to the back of the case. Not deserving of less than a 5 star rating for me as you get what you see here, but that is something that I noticed.
        It's a recommend for me!

        Tyler
        4.0 out of 5 stars Amazing Case, Makes Wireless Charging Difficult
        Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2020
        Color: ClearVerified Purchase
        This case feels extremely sturdy, I really like the fact that the opening around the camera lenses has a bit of a lip to protect them in the event of a fall. It’s extremely clear, time will tell if it will remain clear, I’ve had multiple clear cases almost all of them yellow to an extent so we’ll see what happens in that regard. I also really like that the edge of the case doesn’t interfere with placing a screen protector on the phone at all. There’s just enough space around the edges left for the protector to cover the glass and right where the protector stops the case begins.

        My only real complaint with this case is that the kickstand does impede wireless charging in my experience. A lot of times I can get the wireless charging to work, the thickness of the case isn’t the issue, but the placement of the kickstand does cause some problems. Some times if I play with it and get the placement just right it’ll work fine, other times no matter how much I try to move it around it just will not work. Not a huge issue because the utility of the kickstand outweighs the utility of wireless charging for me, but if that’s a concern it is something to definitely think twice about.
